quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  25,10,"Blessed is the One Who‚ÄĒif He wills‚ÄĒcan give you far better than ňĻallňļ that: gardens under which rivers flow, and palaces as well"
  25,11,"In fact, they deny the Hour.¬†And for the deniers of the Hour, We have prepared a blazing Fire"
